CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 1, 1960, pg. 21, reads: "Everybody's Happy - There wasn't a sad face in all of Pittsburgh Sunday night as the Pittsburgh Pirates, new National League champions, took part in a gigantic victory celebration, following the team's arrival from Milwaukee... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Crowd watching majorettes in parade for celebration of Pittsburgh Pirates' 1960 National League Baseball Championship, Downtown
